{"tid":1350864,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"發現左個扺抗催淚煙嘅方法！","createTime":"2019-07-22T13:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T10:40:45.000Z","uid":3696,"like":7,"dislike":173,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ba3e9966ee9beb85320d324b6cb610a31a53ddcf","tid":1350864,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:55:33.000Z","msg":"話說琴晚發夢係信德前排，隔離個手足帶左豬咀都頂唔順就累低咁，我就反而無乜事一邊膊頭托住佢走咁。<br />\n之後我發現原來佢無食開煙！<br />\n但我就係一個資深煙民！所以我得岀左一個結論<br />\n就係，食多兩口煙 唔怕催淚煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食煙好處其實幾多，打完一輪之後可以食口煙定下驚，又可以係好激動嘅時候食口煙冷靜下，最重要就係平時食煙可以訓練到個喉嚨同個肺扺受到啲高温。<br />\n順帶一提，連我地革命之父，天琦都係食純駱駝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585710c6c652faf1b8b20db278136ba29586b2cf","tid":1350864,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:56:13.000Z","msg":"唔係話教壞你，但真係值得一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd569908841846a79ee164def8754a72cf76ead8","tid":1350864,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:56:33.000Z","msg":"煙民全面進埸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503466edcca21cae5f120da77454b689affe6abf","tid":1350864,"uid":25264,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:15:31.000Z","msg":"強烈要求物資站要有煙仔派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293b1c53c084186eee351c64fd1d8166c9611b8f","tid":1350864,"uid":3696,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"503466edcca21cae5f120da77454b689affe6abf","tid":1350864,"uid":25264,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:15:31.000Z","msg":"強烈要求物資站要有煙仔派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:19:54.000Z","msg":"g持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dfff700729aae5fe65b8740b8f8af76aac13b32","tid":1350864